{"tid":92862,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊思敏係阿妹五倍？莊思明被當玩具：這些錢我沒本事賺","createTime":"2017-01-24T02:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T02:55:10.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"722ea8c984a097a8c101fc794007465fc521db80","tid":92862,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:31:23.000Z","msg":"莊思敏日前喺微博話收到邀請，對方話「100萬玩一夜」，當時已經嬲嬲地，未夠一個星期，唔知係人有樣學樣，竟然有位叫內地網民，再向佢出飯局價，仲開到去「1000萬包夜」，價值十級跳，連莊思敏自己都唔相信值呢個價錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAm0Npr.img?h=410&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=953&amp;y=411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAm0Npr.img%3Fh%3D410%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D953%26y%3D411&h=ad28df47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雲加道歉料被重罰停賽<br />\n無耐莊思敏阿妹莊思明亦喺Instagram貼咗張相，原來又係呢位網民搵佢，仲問莊思明：「可以花兩百萬找你玩嗎」。莊思明睇見就梗係嬲啦，佢喺Instagram留言：「不好意思，我是用多少錢都買不到的，因為我不是一件玩具！這些錢我真的沒本事賺，留給其他人吧！大家以後可以慳番唔使再問我！謝謝！」"},{"pid":"93e1f1869a12e1d89a1a53a0da4fae733d637037","tid":92862,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"on9内容加on9插圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17fe904dde74e6fd1f96a26cddae68f5faf6233","tid":92862,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"大陸會有人識佢哋？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07955647245875a91436e5fc5430e62c4367dcf2","tid":92862,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"條仔幾似莊思明，圖文相符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}